{"brand":{"name":"Camino"},"cannabisStrain":"Indica","cannabisType":"INDICA","description":"We all know what it feels like to be overwhelmed. Cramming for college exams, meeting the demands of a high-pressure work environment, keeping up with endless chores, errands, and childcare responsibilities - though the experiences might seem distinct, the feeling is much the same: overwhelming stress and tension.

Wild Berry “Chill” is crafted for those moments when you need to relax and reset yourself. Each gummy offers a serene escape with THC providing a gentle euphoria to help calm both mind and body complemented by indica-like terpenes for a mellow feeling. As you indulge in the sweet, irresistible berry flavor, feel the tensions of the day melt away with Wild Berry “Chill” Camino gummies.

THC interacts with the body's endocannabinoid system (ECS), influencing neurotransmitter release and binding to cannabinoid receptors, potentially contributing to feelings of relaxation. Its effects on stress response and muscle tension may also promote a sense of calmness and physical ease.

brand.name: &Shine
brand.description: &Shine is all about good cannabis that sparks good times—for anybody, in pretty much any situation. {"brand":{"name":"Camino"},"cannabisStrain":"Sativa","cannabisType":"SATIVA","description":"Have you ever dealt with a demanding schedule, approaching deadlines, and a sense of fatigue creeping in? This is precisely when Camino Sours Tropical Burst Energy gummies step in to give you just the boost you need. Packed with 10MG of THC and 5MG of THCV with sativa-like terpenes and the vitamins B6 and B12 combined with the perfect amount of caffeine (10mg), these gummies are your ticket to an enlivened experience.

THCV is your energy-boosting ally, potentially enhancing metabolism and curbing appetite. It ensures a clear-headed journey ahead.

Vitamin B6 is a prominent player in the body’s energy-production process to give your body the fuel it needs for physical activity.

Vitamin B12 helps keep your body’s blood and nerve cells happy.

Caffeine (10mg per serving), the world’s most popular stimulant, is renowned for its mood-enhancing properties. We add just enough to support increased alertness and a reduction in fatigue, providing a pep in your step equivalent to half a cup of iced tea.

Whether you're about to embark on a thrilling adventure, or simply need a boost to seize the day, Tropical Burst Energy Camino Sours are your go-to choice for an invigorating experience that propels you forward with newfound vitality.

{"brand":{"name":"Camino"},"cannabisStrain":"Hybrid","cannabisType":"HYBRID","description":"In the midst of life's chaos, from juggling stress at work to navigating personal relationships, it's no wonder we sometimes find ourselves feeling off-kilter and in need of grounding. When stress weighs heavy and you're yearning to reclaim your sense of equilibrium, turn to Mango Serenity 'Balance' Camino gummies.

The harmonious combo of 5MG THC and 5MG CBD creates a welcomed shift in your perspective- almost like discovering a hidden Zen garden landscape right in your own background.

THC, often associated with feelings of euphoria, plays a role in promoting balance and well-being.

CBD, most known for its calming effects, works synergistically with THC to promote a sense of tranquility and equilibrium without overstimulation.

As you indulge in the sweet tropical flavors of ripe mango, you'll feel tension melt away and a wave of serenity wash over you. brand.name: Encore
brand.description: The show goes on. Like a song that takes you back, Encore Edibles are all timeless hits. Finding comfort in the familiar, these terpene-enriched treats come in classic flavor profiles, reminiscent of your old-school favorites. Offered in a variety of formats, doses, and cannabinoid ratios, our hand-crafted cannabis gummies, hard candies, mints, caramels, and chocolates taste as good as they feel.

variants.name: Encore Espresso Caramels - 100mg
variants.description:
Up the tempo any time of day with Espresso Sativa Caramels. Crafted with an infusion of terpenes for uplifting, euphoric, and energizing effects, these Caramels are sure to be a weekend favorite. And don’t worry – we chose our favorite espresso beans for the most delightful coffee caramel fusion.

Skip the cream and sugar for a caramel or two. These delicious edibles melt perfectly into your favorite cuppa, whether coffee or espresso, and cut the bitterness while enhancing the delicate undertones of your favorite beans.

brand.name: Beboe
brand.description:
My grandmother’s name was Be Boe. My mother was diagnosed with cancer when I was very young and my grandmother visited frequently to help care for her. She cleaned up the house and cooked for us.

One thing she made each trip were brownies. She made one tray for us kids, and one tray for Mom, but Mom’s brownies were strictly off limits…kept under lock and key in a closet. Of course we would go through our rations in 24 hours, turning our sights on mom’s reserve. We were reminded each time that mom was really sick, deserved to have her own brownies, and backed off.

We found out years later that mom’s brownies were made with marijuana. They would help the nausea brought on by the sickness and brought back her appetite. I laugh every time I imagine that little 85 year old woman wandering around our local grocer, trying to find someone who could help her buy a bag of weed.

In appreciation of all she did to bring warmth and love into our house, we started Beboe to offer the sophisticated cannabis consumer an experience unlike any other on the market.

Strain Notes:
Get ready to ride a wave of euphoric creativity. A cross of Sunset Sherbert and Kush Mintz 11, the indica-dominant hybrid strain Sunset Mintz is like a jammy berry journey of grape and sass.


Lost Farm is the first edibles brand made with strain-specific 100% live resin, which retains the delicate cannabinoids, flavonoids, and terpenes in the plant to deliver a distinctively brighter and more complex full-spectrum edibles experience. At the time of harvest, cannabis flower is flash-frozen to preserve the rich flavors, complex aromas, and broad terpene profiles typically lost in the drying and curing process. From there, the flower is delicately extracted to create the most true-to-plant cannabis extract possible.

• Après Ski snacking

• Soothing the Sunday scaries
